            "created_at": "2018-01-08T18:47:40Z",
            "updated_at": "2018-01-08T18:47:40Z",
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "@miguelgrinberg so the plan is to deprecate `debug=True` in anything but config vars.\r\n\r\nThe reason environments are important is that everything currently uses debug to indicate development mode which is a terrible idea once ngrok and other things are involved. It's important to be able to turn off insecure debug features independently of leaving the development environment. Likewise right now we only have prod vs debug and that does not scale well enough to the real world."
        },
