            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> So I want to establish a common flag that indicates \"this is development\" without dangerous tools being forcefully enabled.\r\n\r\nIsn't this what `app.config['DEBUG'] = True` does?\r\n\r\nAs I said, I don't mind environments, but I don't see a reason to use them myself. The default of `production` that you picked may confuse people, but at least allows those who don't care to just ignore it and everything still works in the expected way."
